OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Ffine end to the day, with bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Leading into a dry, warm
OL,8,Fand muggy night with variable amounts
OL,9,Fof cloud, clear spells and light
OL,10,Fwinds. Perhaps becoming mostly cloudy
OL,11,Ftowards dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FEarly cloud will soon thin
OL,14,Fand break up to give a mostly fine day
OL,15,Fwith bright or sunny spells for many.
OL,16,FFeeling very warm and muggy. Light
OL,17,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
