OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,6,Ffine with some sunshine. Turning very
OL,7,Fwarm and humid towards the weekend,
OL,8,Fstaying mainly dry, but with a small
OL,9,Fchance of some scattered showers on
OL,10,FSaturday.
